mily:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 안아줘요 조준으로 최대한 죽이기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">그 후 방깎 랩처 1마리 제외하고 죽이기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">2-1. 레후 1뎀~2자리수뎀 뜰 경우</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">계속 리트하면서 데미지 빌드 만들기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">영상에서 버프창 확인한 이유는 크라운 힐로 들어오는 공뎀 20.99% 확인 용도 (없어야함)</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">내 기준 데미지 빌드는</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 수니스 2스 2번 853334 * 2</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 레후 풀차지 1번 60679</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 레후 160~174% 차지샷 1번 36344</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">한번이라도&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">크리 뜨면 리트</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">1803691 에서 추가로 +1000~2000 데미지 넣기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 대략 체력이 1805000 인듯</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">영상에서는 빨리 죽을줄 모르고 크라운 스택 많이 안쌓여있고 체력 다 회복 못했음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 다행히 다음 신데렐라 곡사포가 첫 안아줘요 없애서 살았음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">3. 나가로 피채우기</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">최대 18초 남았을때 잡아아함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 그 뒤로 잡으면 보스 등장이 10초 미만이 되어버림</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">4. 레후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">신데렐라 쓰면 바로 3번째 뿡뿡이 나옴</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32c